  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dd1\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db6\u0dd9\u0daf\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "President tells officials how to distribute gas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa instructed the officials today (10) to carry out the unloading and distribution of gas promptly.",
        "The first ship carrying 3700 metric tons of gas reached Sri Lanka yesterday (10) and the second ship carrying 3740 metric tons of gas is scheduled to arrive this afternoon (10), according to the President's Office.",
        "The office also mentions that the third ship carrying 3200 metric tons of gas will arrive in Sri Lanka on the 15th.",
        "The amount of gas ordered for this month is 33,000 metric tons.",
        "Mr. Muditha Peiris, Chairman of Litro Company, said that gas distribution will be done as normal and systematically from the 12th and the problem regarding domestic gas demand will be completely avoided by the end of this month."
      ],
